Popular Nollywood actor, Dejo Tunfulu is dead. His death was confirmed by his friend and fellow actor, Kunle Afod. He, however, failed to reveal the cause of his death. Popular radio presenter, Adeyemi Olabode, also mourning his death wrote on his Facebook page: “I saw the post about your demise and hurriedly called your line so you can debunk the ‘April fool’ news, but alas! Your son picked it. “You were so kind and down to earth. “You are one of the few I do lean on in the entertainment industry. I cannot do without disturbing you with my weekly BC messages on Whatsapp. So we would not be able to speak again Egbon. “So our plans won’t be again? Rest in peace Dejo Tunfulu.”